TO ALL NEW DRIVERS AND SOON-TO-BE NEW DRIVERS:

BEWARE OF IDIOTIC DRIVERS ON THE ROAD!!!!!!!!!!!!

this fucking idiotic pick-up driver annoyed the hell out of me. firstly his right signal was perpetually flashing. then, he was indecisive in filtering to the CTE(City) lane. then, HE STOPPED ON THE HIGHWAY AS HE PLEASED!! and blocked the entire one lane carriageway. like seriously what the fuck??? you deserve to tio horn you asshole!! FYI, i honked u damn loud too. KNN.

i am not usually this vulgar but precisely because i am a new driver and i have many other friends and relatives who are soon to be new drivers, i am ADDITIONALLY pissed. 


go to hell you fucker

i really ought to thank the heavens and earths for letting me pass today. everything went well during the warm up, but i kinda cocked up during the actual test itself. let me tell you why.

i was super hungry to start with. my tummy was growling away while waiting for the testers to come. went to the car and was super nervous. did reaction-response and it was OMFG. because it was raining, the kerb was went and i couldn't really mount the kerb. had to come down and accelerate up a second time. at this point of time, stress level: 3/5.

then went on to do directional change which was pretty alright i guess. then the horror came. went to do vertical parking, and retarded me full locked the steering wheel when the front right pole disappeared, WHICH IS SO DARN WRONG BECAUSE THATS THE METHOD FOR PARALLEL PARKING!!! totally freaked out a drove out of the lot again, repositioned my car and attempted to reverse into the lot. THEN, i struck the kerb. which is like WTF la. i NEVER had this problem please. stress level: 6/5.

went to do parallel parking. that was fine, directional change, was okay too. then went out to the road to start on my test route 1. there was a stupid mini-jam just after turning left out of the school and going all the way straight. so, tester decided to turn left into the small road. then he proceeded to direct me back to driving school.

thoughts at this point of time: die cheryl-jo tan. you failed your driving test you loser.

stopped the car inside the yellow box at the front lobby and went up to the 2nd level with the tester to get my results. he sat me down and smiled and said, "luckily you were wise enough to reposition your car when you realised that you did v. parking wrongly. can't really assess how good you are on the road because the traffic so heavy. i let you pass la."

WOOT. 10 demerit points. hahaha nice tester!!

i bet my mummy, ahgong and everyone else blessed me like crap. what more can i say?? HAHA.

I'M A CLASS 3A DRIVER AS OF TODAY. =D

i must say that skills are not all that matter. just look at mine la. he could have easily failed me but he didn't. i guess looking confident really matters.

and, i wanna do plastic surgery! haven't even gone through any of the procedures before but am already tres hooked to it. if it makes you happy, boosts your self confidence, i dont see why not! its ur face, ur life, ur money. why would anyone (except ur parents mebbi; they created you) be bothered? don't people just wanna look at pretty and pleasant things? i admit im not nice to look at, so i must change this ma!

haha.. anyways!! my traffic police test is not that far away. 17 days away to be precise. my skills are more or less there, just that im not that mentally ready for it. seriously hope i dont freak out on that day. i wanna pass on my first try! dont wanna waste money retaking it and waste time waiting for another test date. its not as if i hadn't wasted enuff time on driving itself.

signing off,

Lifestory: When Dick meets Pussy
It is not a sin to have a dick or a pussy. But it's a sin if you're one.

SCENE 1

Dick: hey, i was thinking, shall we go for a short trip to like, let's say, Genting?!! together with your girl. i'll bring a girl too!
Loser: wow, that sounds cool. but you have a girl in your heart now?
Dick: no, i have no girl in my heart currently, in fact, ever! but i do have a lot of girls on my mind!!

Dick and Loser laugh together heartily.

Dick: i really cant wait to meet your girl!

Loser smiles to himself at the thought of his beauty.

SCENE 2

Loser: hey, this is Pussy.
Pussy: hello! (batter eyelashes flirtatiously)
Dick: hi! i'm er, Dick! (shakes hand with Pussy and stroke her hand fondly)
Loser: oh, so this is Diana?
Diana: hi~ (smiles shyly)

Loser, Pussy, Dick and Diana spent their day having lots of fun at Genting Highlands.They soon blossomed into close friends.
Or at least, Diana naively thought so...

SCENE 3

Diana: we're sharing bedrooms? i thought it'd be Pussy and me? i like her. (smiles at the thought of that)
Dick: nah, let Loser and Pussy sleep together. (winks) you know...
Diana: but i thought they're not attached yet?
Dick: it doesnt matter right? we're also not attached but yet we're sharing room.

Dick leans over and kisses Diana.
Diana thought to herself, oh.. so he really likes me...
Diana wakes up from her thought and quickly pushes Dick away.
Dick tries his luck again and is rejected by Diana.
Damn it! Dick mutters under his breath.

SCENE 4

Dick, Loser, Pussy, Diana: YEAH~ we are the inseparable Malaysia 4!! we'll meet up for meals whenever we are all free. we'll all be super close friends. YEAH~

SCENE 5

Pussy: hey. please dont fall sick again. do take very good care of yourself. i miss you! hugs. cant wait to see you again.
Dick: haha. you sweet little thing.
Pussy: gosh. i'm being sweet again! please quickly come, sit beside me and talk to me when the 4 of us meet up again alright. i want pictures of us!
Dick: sure baby, but we need to be discreet.

* * *
Pussy: hey, i think Dick really treats you differently from other girls.
Diana: haha. what do you mean?
Pussy: do you like him? tell me! we're BFF! you like him, dont you!! (giggles excitedly)
Diana: oh, stop teasing me! (blushes)

* * *
Pussy: i think our relationships are getting too messy. i think Diana is very much in love with you. all these shall end when the both of them go for their hall camps.
Dick: oh no. come on baby, you know you want me too.
Pussy: oh, stop it~ (giggles)

* * *
Dick, Pussy, Loser, Diana: YEAH, we are the Malaysia 4!!

SCENE 6

Pussy: oh no, Loser found out about us. he even told me i'm not your type. shrugs. whatever.
Dick: he doesnt mind?
Pussy: he's an idiot who loves me too much to mind. cant you even tell that he doesnt mind me going on dates with other guys as well? anyway i still do let him hold my hand, hug me, kiss me, why should he complain?
Dick: yea, what about Diana?
Pussy: come on, she's just another one of your cheap flings.
Dick: haha. dont call them that! they're all just friends. i am free to date many many girls at one time. no obligations~ anyway, i do spend money on them ok. i buy expensive presents.
Pussy: ya. and then you kiss them, hug them and hold their hands. you bastard! (laughs a little)
Dick: well well, birds of the same feathers flock together. i miss you darling.
Pussy: oh... you make me so wanna kiss and hug you right now!

SCENE 7

Loser: you know i love you no matter what. you will come back to me when you finally see that Dick is not serious about you at all.
Pussy: who cares. i am not even into serious relationships, you know that.
Loser: after all that i've done, cant you tell that i will love you no matter what. even if i hold the very same hand my buddy holds, kiss the very same forehead and lips my buddy kisses, hug the girl my buddy hugs.
Pussy: aww... Loser! (hugs Loser)

SCENE 8

Pussy's birthday is round the corner...
Diana:i mustnt fall asleep, no, i must finish this by tonight. hope pussy likes this handmade scroll.
Diana's roomie: hey, sleep early okay? it's already 3am you crazy girl! you've been up whole week rushing projects and studying for tests. you can do that another time!
Diana: no, it's Pussy's birthday tomorrow, i wanna surprise her. hopes she likes the doggie bracelet me and Dick bought her. she really loves dogs you know.
D's roomie: by the way, dick didnt buy that with you! it was me who went around looking for that with you! haha. and you even went around asking for Elmo soft toy. i bet she'll love the bracelet more than an Elmo soft toy! she's already 19!
Diana: true. but Pussy really likes Elmo too!
D's roomie: yes yes, i can already memorise what she likes or not like, she's your new best friend and you're really glad you met the Malaysia 4...
Diana: you're jealous!!
D's roomie: no i'm not! i'm glad you made great friends but i still dont feel good about Dick!!
Diana: you're jealous! (giggles)

Diana's and her roomie's laughter fades off into the late dark night.

SCENE 9

Diana, Loser, Dick: Happy Birthday to Pussy~
Pussy: thank you!! (smiles happily)
Diana, Loser, Dick, Pussy: Malaysia 4, yeah!

SCENE 10

Dick: i need to borrow books from your school's library. can you get them for me and bring down to my school for me?
Diana: but it's so inconvenient... well, alright, since we're such close friends, i'm willing to bring them down for you.
Dick: great. thanks!
Ha! Another stupid girl who is willing to do anything for me. Dick, you really have a way with girls! Dick grins at the thought of that.

* * *
One stormy night, when the bag can no longer hold the hyperactive cat, when the paper lantern caught fire, when the beans spill, Diana cannot believe how all these can be possible, how she has been kept in the dark for so long, how she had treated them like part of her.

They had been wonderful actors. Or was it that she was too blinded and naive to notice anything fishy.

Diana realises that she might have accidentally fallen in love with Dick. The way he plants light kisses on her face, the way he hugs her protectively, the way he pretends to care, they are all nothing but a pack of ugly lies. How she thought Pussy is her confidante, soul mate. How the Malaysia 4 is her lunch khakis, BFF.

The great pretence, it broke her heart into pieces.

Diana fought back her tears.

Diana learnt her lessons. She has decided to stay away from those people she once thought were friends. They are actually nothing more than a bunch of croaches, rats and toads.

Diana was thankful for her other wonderful friends, real friends, who supported her, stood by her no matter what. They love her for who she is, never took advantage of her kindness, never put up a masquerade, who have been truthful, honest and respected her. Diana continues to live her life happily with friends, real friends, humans.

And you wonder, what happened to Dick, Pussy and Loser then?

Dick: hey, Diana has left us. i kind of miss her.
Pussy: me too... but you'd better miss me more!!
Loser: hey, please dont forget i'm here okay!
Dick: sorry dude, hey, i've been wanting to ask you guys this for quite some time...
Pussy: what?
Dick: you two, interested in threesome?
Loser: well, i dont mind, if it is what Pussy wants. i'll do anything for her. even if it means to brokeback my best buddy.
Pussy got really agitated.
Pussy: hello?! mind you!
Dick: oh come on, i was just asking, why get so worked up?
Pussy: threesome is better if it's 2 girls and 1 guy, not the other way round! can you find another girl? Loser can be the cameraman.
Loser: anything, just for you my true love...
Dick: you two are crazy!
Dick walked off suddenly.
Loser, Pussy: hey!! so is it still on?!~
Dick rolled his eyes and left to plan for an orgy with all his ex/current flings.

THE END

just a very lame little story i wrote.
the story is purely fiction. any coincidence is unintended.
hope you enjoyed the story~
